Frontend (your calendar UI)
      ↓ fetch/post requests
Backend (Node.js Express API)
      ↓
Database (MongoDB Atlas)


hoa-calendar/
│
├── /frontend
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── styles.css
│   └── script.js
│
├── /api
│   └── events.js      ← Express API routes
│
├── package.json
├── vercel.json        ← Deployment config
└── .env               ← MongoDB credentials (not committed)


